data.description: **5+ acres, waterfront** Own a home that makes you feel like you are on vacation! House offers East and West exposures so you can enjoy sunrises on your front porch every morning and beautiful sunsets over a private 650 acre lake from your back porch each evening.  Wildlife and nature at its finest!  Entire 5+ acre property is fenced (except for waterfront).  Home has split floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths.  Large open kitchen with island, plenty of cabinet storage space, and water filtration system.  Water softener system installed in 2017.  New metal roof in 2015.  Three-quarters of home has a wrap around porch with back portion screened in (rescreened in 2021).  200ft lake front access with beach area - enjoy relaxing by the lake, fishing, boating, kayaking, jet skiing, and more!  Property also offers a shed and 40x60 3-bay building with half-bath, shelving and work bench.  Excellent location - 25 miles east of Gainesville and 1 hour from St. Augustine and the Atlantic beaches!  Motivated sellers moving for work and school, make an offer!
